name: rooftop pictures
description: "rooftop pictures" is part of the #OBJKT4OBJKT event. | Created by arthur (a teacher in Shanghai) & owae.ga (a multimedia artist from Switzerland) Photo is shot on a Ricoh Half-frame with Portra 400, video is created by owae.ga. The combination creates a personality, a character, for each of these photos that makes you contemplate what their experience is like and how they think. Find both artists on twitter @ryanartwalker and @owae_
